  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/news/\" rel=\"tag\">科技新闻</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/03/11/hitachi-emiew-2-robot-human-collisions/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://o.aolcdn.com/hss/storage/adam/532f73fe1845dec9fede4a661fca9aa0/hitachi-emiew-2-people-avoidance-2014-03-14-01.jpg\" style=\"width: 620px; height: 354px;\" /></a></div>\n\n<div><br />\n日立旗下的 <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2010/06/23/hitachi-debuts-emiew-2-robot/\">Emiew 2</a> 机器人又「<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2012/02/22/emiew-2-connects-to-the-internet-wants-to-google-your-stuff-vi/\">进化</a>」了，这次它身上多出了一个可以测定行进速度的感应器。基于搜集到的数据，系统会自动预测可能会出现行人的位置，并且生成相应的地图数据让 Emiew 2 避免碰撞（直接避开或减速）。但实话说，Emiew 2 的身高不足 1 米，速度也就大约每秒 1.7 米，真被它撞到应该也不会有太严重的后果啦（又不是都像 <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2011/10/03/boston-dynamics-alpha-dog-makes-alyx-vances-pet-look-like-a-toy/\">BigDog</a> 那么吓人...）。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n经由：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2014/03/11/hitachi-emiew-2-robot-human-collisions/\">Engadget</a><br />\n引用来源：<span class=\"source\"><a href=\"http://asia.nikkei.com/Tech-Science/Tech/Hitachi-robot-avoids-unpleasant-run-ins-with-pedestrians\" target=\"_blank\">Nikkei</a></span></div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/03/11/hitachi-emiew-2-robot-human-collisions/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20847275/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/03/11/hitachi-emiew-2-robot-human-collisions/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><hr size=\"1\" />", 
